 null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000495, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Call Ali, The Manifestor of Wonders Thou shalt find him a helper unto thee in thy difficulties Presently all worries and sorrows will be removed By thy Greatness O Lord By thy Apostleship o Muhammad By thy Authority O Ali, O Ali, O Ali Come to my help!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ajaaeb Khuda ke jalwa'e bardaar Ali ibne Abi Talib (a.s) ko zara pukaar to sahih. Tum har museebat aur balaawo’n mein unko apna Mushkil Kusha paawoge. Ay Allah Teri azmat ke waaste se aur Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aap ki nabuwat ke sadqe aur Hazrat Ali (a.s) aap ki wilayat ke wasile se mere tamaam ranj o gham museebate’n dur ho. Ya Ali! Ya Ali! Ya Ali!", "Urdu": "عجائب خدا کے جلوہ بردار علی ابن ابی طالبؑ کو ذرا پکارو تو سہی تم ہر مصیبت و بلا میں ان کو اپنا مشکلکشا پاؤگے۔ اے محمدؐ آپ کی نبوت اور اے علیؑ آپ کی ولایت سے چونکہ تمام رنج و غم کی مصیبتیں حاجتمندوں کی ناصیہ حاجت سے صاف ہو جاتی ہیں اس لئے عرض ہے کہ ہماری خبر لیجئے۔", "RArabic": "NAADE A’LIYYAN MAZHARAL A’JAAA-EBE TAJIDHO A’WNAN LAKA FIN NAWAAA-EBE KULLO HAMMIWN WA GHAMMIN SAYANJALEE BE-A’ZAMATEKA YAA ALLAAHO BE NOBUWWATEKA YAA MOHAMMADO BE WELAAYATEKA YAA A’LIYYO YAA A’LIYYO YAA A’LIYYO.", "ArabicText1": "نَادِ عَلِیًّا مَّظْھَرَ الْعَجَآئِبِ تَجِدْہٗ عَوْنًا لَّكَ فِیْ النَّوَآئِبِ كُلُّ ھَمٍّ وَّغَمٍّ سَیَنْجَلِیْ بِعَظَمَتِكَ یَااَللہُ بِنُبُوَّتِكَ یَامُحَمَّدُ بِوِلَایَتِكَ یَاعَلِیُّ یَاعَلِیُّ یَاعَلِیُّ۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": n